Author: icd
Title: [ANN] [ICO] S4FE: World’s first blockchain for stolen goods
Body: S4FE (https://s4fe.io) S4FE is the world’s first blockchain technology based global database for the registration and identification of stolen or lost items. The database is accessible to everyone and enables users to register and search property on the blockchain. Such property could be electronic devices, jewelry, collections, valuables of any kind, documents, sports and hobby equipment, vehicles and machines or nearly any conceivable item representing a value to its owner.
